            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Iulius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> |(mulieris) <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> Faustus <lb n="2"/>Caecilia |(mulieris) <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>iberta</ex></expan> Iucunda <lb n="3"/>o fortuna hominum dubia quae fata gubernas <lb n="4"/>cur me privasti Iulio Fausto <lb n="5"/>cenanti trichileis symphonia suave canebat <lb n="6"/>nunc infelici tundit Cerberus auriculas <lb n="7"/>si quicquam pietatis habes sanctissima mater <lb n="8"/>subleva me abiectum a finibus Tartariis <lb n="9"/>pristina cura domo fama decoratus quievit <lb n="10"/>nunc me Cerberus ducit in exitium <lb n="11"/>Fauste venuste vale niveo decoratus marite <lb n="12"/>otia luxuriae vincula perdidimus <lb n="13"/>gaudia matris acerba patris querumonia <note>sic</note> maesta <lb n="14"/>me iam tot ad cinerem cornua rauca vocant <lb n="15"/>viginti et sexto me Cluthes <note>sic</note> duxit in annos <lb n="16"/>hunc finem Parcae sorte dedere mihi
            </ab></div>
